      <p class="kids">My name is Michael Geldorp. I am 32 years old, and I live 
      in a small town in the Netherlands. I have liked astronomy since 
      I was 8 years old. I own a 
      telescope, and I try to go out under the stars when it is clear at 
      night. Instead of just looking at a planet or a nebula and forgetting 
      it later, I always draw what I see.</p>
      
