      <p class="kids">After drawing for a few minutes, 
      you will see much more than you thought at first. Drawing really 
      makes you appreciate the beauty of the night sky.</p>
      
      <p class="kids">Drawing looks hard, but it's really easy. You don’t 
      need to be an artist to do it; it just takes a little practice. Remember, 
      your drawing doesn’t have to be pretty. Just make the sketch look 
      as much like the real object as you can.</p>
      
      <p class="kids">On the next page, I'll try to explain how I draw what 
      I see. I hope these tips will help you with your drawings.</p>
      
